  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took me back to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- how do you call a hospital where there is only soldiers there?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Yes, I was taken there, and because I was the only woman logged into a room, a separate room, and they always [? unlocked ?] the room and they give me food.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they always looked after themselves so I couldn't escape or go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] After a while, when my boss's wife found me--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the hospital.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was going from step to step until she found me that I am in the hospital and they let her in to visit me and she notified my husband.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, my husband was also because-- she was a Jewish man, she was escaping in a soldier's uniform with-- with false papers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I wasn't married then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Steven [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Heimann ?] then, but he already called himself [INAUDIBLE] because he was escaping with false papers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was working-- as a matter of fact, this-- this school where I finished, the Jewish school, they made into a press for false papers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was working there, and he was distributing that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sorry I didn't-- I have got a-- it's a funny thing I just remembered.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I have got [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] insert from my book, which-- from Israel, and, in that book, my husband does mention what a good deed he made with the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he sent me a copy of this page to see and show it to my family because he was like a hero.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was risking his life, and he went from place to place to distribute, wherever it was necessary, and he-- he could reach people.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
